headline: Dover Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date, Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Dover (NYSE: DOV) announced today that it will release first quarter 2025 earnings at approximately 6:00 a.m. Central time (7:00 a.m. Eastern time) on Thursday, April 24, 2025. Later that morning, Dover will host a conference call at 8:30 a.m. Central time (9:30 a.m. Eastern time) to discuss these results.

headline: Dover (DOV) Surges 9.7%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Dover (DOV) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
